name: SVGCursorElement
description: The SVGCursorElement interface provides access to the properties of <cursor> elements, as well as methods to manipulate them.

members.name: SVGCursorElement.x
members.description: An SVGAnimatedLength corresponding to the x attribute of the given <cursor> element.

members.name: SVGCursorElement.y
members.description: An SVGAnimatedLength corresponding to the y attribute of the given <cursor> element.
